title: AlphaTALKS Wall Street Breakfast September 25: What Moved Markets This Week
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: It was a volatile week, with the Federal Reserve meeting to announce interest rate policy and unfolding drama from China -- first around Evergrande (OTCPK:EGRNF) and then cryptocurrencies. Bond yields shot up after the market digested the Fed move to all but telegraph tapering of bond purchases.
